							<div class="social-container notransition">
								<div class="social-likes social-likes_notext" data-title="The Man Who Found Stuxnet – Sergey Ulasen in the Spotlight" data-url="https://eugene.kaspersky.com/2011/11/02/the-man-who-found-stuxnet-sergey-ulasen-in-the-spotlight/" data-counters="no" data-zeroes="yes"><div class="facebook" title="Share via Facebook"></div>
<div class="linkedin" title="Share via LinkedIn"></div>
<div class="twitter" title="Share via Twitter"></div></div>							</div>
							<div class='plus closed'>
